			<ns0:name>pol...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/101953680983947802512/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">How-to
1) Move [mime_type + is_extension_url] check from FileDownloader to PluginPpapi. E.g. it can be done on initialization and stored in some member var with a getter.
2) Change FileDownloader to use it.
3) BrowserPpp::InitializeModule sets global PPB_GetInterface pointer using SetPPBGetInterface. Extend it to store the above setting as well.
4) It is now accessible from GetBrowserInterface.
